  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Global Subjects Global Issues</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">U&#x10D;&#xED;me (sa) v glob&#xE1;lnych s&#xFA;vislostiach 2</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Cie&#x13E;om projektu je 1) zv&#xFD;&#x161;i&#x165; particip&#xE1;ciu slovensk&#xFD;ch u&#x10D;ite&#x13E;ov a u&#x10D;iteliek pri za&#x10D;le&#x148;ovan&#xED; glob&#xE1;lneho rozvojov&#xE9;ho vzdel&#xE1;vania (&#x10F;alej &#x201C;GRV&#x201D;) do vzdel&#xE1;vac&#xED;ch procesov, s d&#xF4;razom na implement&#xE1;ciu Cie&#x13E;ov udr&#x17E;ate&#x13E;n&#xE9;ho rozvoja. &#x10E;al&#x161;&#xED;m cie&#x13E;om je 2) podpora budovania kapac&#xED;t u&#x10D;ite&#x13E;ov pri pr&#xED;prave a realiz&#xE1;cii aktiv&#xED;t GRV. U&#x10D;itelia si v&#x10F;aka projektu rozvin&#xFA; svoje zru&#x10D;nosti a kompetencie pri tvorbe a realiz&#xE1;cii glob&#xE1;lnovzdel&#xE1;vac&#xED;ch aktiv&#xED;t nielen &#xFA;&#x10D;as&#x165;ou na viacd&#x148;ov&#xFD;ch &#x161;koleniach, ale aj pomocou metodicko-didaktick&#xFD;ch materi&#xE1;lov kop&#xED;ruj&#xFA;cich &#x161;t&#xE1;tny vzdel&#xE1;vac&#xED; program.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the project is 1) to increase the participation of Slovak teachers in the integration of Global Development Education (&quot;GDE&quot;) into educational processes with emphasis on the implementation of Sustainable Development Goals. Another objective is 2) to support teacher&#xB4;s capacity building in the preparation and implementation of GRV activities. Through the project activities teachers will develop and improve their skills and competences in the creation and implementation of global education activities not only by participating in multidisciplinary trainings but also by using methodological and didactic materials which are corresponding with the state educational program.</narrative>
  </description>
